long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Job Mentor AI is a AI enabled platform that helps job seeking candidates to prepare for and excel their interviews by generating custom practice Q&A and also by facilitating real-time Mock Interviews for practice. It uses the latest realtime AI engine to facilitate interview practice to replicate the real interview. 

>> Custom cover letter generation to ease application process.
>> Customized practice and question set for different jobs.
>> Realtime mock interview with AI that replicates real world interview scenario.

Practice and boost your confidence today!
